  "blurb": "A five-bedroom cliffside villa on Kamala's Millionaire's Mile, with four infinity pools stepping toward panoramic views of the Andaman Sea. Media room, gym and yoga space, estate beach access and daily breakfast sit across some 2,220 m², with a five-strong team and a private chef, sleeping up to twelve.",
  "detail": "Perched on the cliffs of Kamala's Millionaire's Mile, this five-bedroom villa is a study in privacy and open horizon — a secluded run of terraces looking out over the Andaman Sea, five minutes from Kamala Beach. Three of the bedrooms have their own private pool; two further guest rooms complete the house.\n\nFour infinity pools step down the site, each catching a different angle of the water, with an outdoor gazebo for shaded lounging between them. Estate beach access is half a kilometre away, and a pickleball court is shared within the community.\n\nIndoors, across roughly 2,220 m² of villa, a media room with karaoke, a gym and yoga room, a fully equipped kitchen and generous living spaces open to the view. Six flatscreen televisions with cable and Netflix, high-speed WiFi and a BBQ round out the house, with indoor and outdoor dining oriented to the sunset.\n\nA team of five, including a private chef, runs the villa, with complimentary daily breakfast, housekeeping, turndown, return airport transfers and 24-hour estate security included; car hire, spa, laundry and a wine list are available on request.",
